third person.<br></li><li> Sit at the helm and take the ship for a spin. Why not try and see if you too can &quot;hug the donkey&quot;?<br></li><li> Jump into multiplayer with a few friends and explore the ship together. Alternatively you can pick up a Longbow and test out your marksmanship on them. <br></li><li> Visit the E-Sim and go bowling, or visit Bortus' &quot;special&quot; program, if you can find it!<br></li><li> Character customisation. Be who you want to be! <br></li><li> Synthesise a few nick-knacks at any of the ship's matter synthesizers. Pick them up and place them freely. Why not give Bortus and Clyden's quarters a quick spruce up?<br></li><li> Take in the breathtaking views out of the Mess Hall windows of the Planetary Union Dockyard in Earth orbit.<br></li><li> Customize your own quarters and upload it to the Steam Workshop for everyone to marvel at!<br></li><li> Send the ship into disarray with a variety of different alert modes, each changing the ambiance throughout the ship. Find the one that best suits your mood. Or perhaps you've just got the urge to party like a Moclan?<br></li><li> Completely original score with undertones and themes from the show by the legendary Patrick Phillips.<br></li><li> In-game chat for both text and voice in Multiplayer games. All in aid of the great Orville community spirit.<br></li><li> Wander down to the Shuttle Bay and take a shuttle out for a joyride.<br></li><li> Fight Kaylon ships in the Unknown Sector.</li></ul>","developers":["Messy Desk Interactive"],"genres":[{"description":"Casual","id":"4"},{"description":"Simulation","id":"28"},{"description":"Free To Play","id":"37"},{"description":"Early Access","id":"70"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1096200/header.jpg?t=1726341696","is_free":true,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"m